    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "已知 $P\\left(X = x_{i}\\right) = p_{i}, i = 1, \\ldots, n$ 。根据以上概率分布抽取 100 个样本。",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            296,
            893,
            450
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} > x <   - c (\\dots); p <   - c (\\dots); n <   - l e n g t h (x) \\\\ > \\text {i n d e x} <   - \\text {s a m p l e} (1: n, 1 0 0, \\text {r e p l a c e} = T, \\text {p r o b} = p); x _ {\\text {s a m p l e}} <   - x [ \\text {i n d e x} ] \\\\ > x \\_ s a m p l e <   - s a m p l e (x, 1 0 0, r e p l a c e = T, p r o b = p) \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            296,
            893,
            918
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "连续型随机变量",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            140,
            444,
            238
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "已知 $X$ 密度函数为 $f(x)$ 。根据以上密度函数抽取 100 个样本。",
        "bbox": [
            67,
            288,
            815,
            357
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "在 $X$ 的支撑（取值范围，设为 $[a, b]$ ）内均匀地“打格子点”，即令 $a = x_{1} \\leq \\cdots \\leq x_{n} = b$ ，且 $x_{i}$ 的间隔一样，并计算 $p_{i} = f(x_{i})$ ，然后按离散概率的抽样方式从 $x_{i}$ 中抽取 100 个样本即可。",
        "bbox": [
            63,
            525,
            933,
            783
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "连续型随机变量",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            444,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} P (X = x _ {i}) \\approx P (x _ {i} \\leq X \\leq x _ {i} + \\Delta x) = P (X \\leq x _ {i} + \\Delta x) - P (X \\leq x _ {i}) = \\\\ F (x _ {i} + \\Delta x) - F (x _ {i}) = F ^ {\\prime} (\\xi) \\cdot \\Delta x = f (\\xi) \\cdot \\Delta x \\approx f (x _ {i}) \\Delta x \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            75,
            294,
            915,
            448
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\xi \\in [ x _ {i}, x _ {i} + \\Delta x ]\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            75,
            505,
            272,
            562
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "可见， $P(X = x_{i}) \\propto f(x_{i})$ 。",
        "bbox": [
            79,
            735,
            416,
            794
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "例：从U(0,1)中抽取样本",
