    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二维离散型随机向量",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            140,
            544,
            240
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "已知 $P\\left(X = x_{i}, Y = y_{j}\\right) = p_{ij}, i = 1, \\ldots, I; j = 1, \\ldots, J$ 。根据以上概率分布抽取 100 个样本。",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            303,
            922,
            466
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "把数据矩阵“拉直”为一个向量，即令 $P(Z = k) = P\\big(X = x_{i}, Y = y_{j}\\big), k = 1,2,\\ldots,I \\times J$ ，并记此概率为 $\\tilde{p}_{k}$ 。然后按照离散型随机变量的方式抽取100个 $Z$ 的样本，并把 $k$ 对应回 $x_{i}$ 和 $y_{j}$ 即可。",
        "bbox": [
            81,
            592,
            922,
            894
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二维离散型随机向量",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            542,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "$>\\mathrm{x}<-\\mathrm{c}(\\ldots);\\mathrm{y}<-\\mathrm{c}(\\ldots);\\mathrm{l}<-\\mathrm{length}(\\mathrm{x});\\mathrm{J}<-\\mathrm{length}(\\mathrm{y})$ ",
            "> $p<-matrix(..., nrow=1, ncol=J)$ ",
            "> p2<-as.vector(p) #注：按列拉直 ",
            "> index<-sample(1:(I*J), 100, replace=T, prob=p2) ",
            "> index1<- (index-1)%%|+1; index2<- (index-1)%%|+1 ",
            "> data_sample<-cbind(x[index1], y[index2]) "
        ],
        "bbox": [
            84,
            300,
            709,
            879
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二维离散型随机向量",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            140,
            544,
            238
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "1. 计算 $X$ 的边缘概率，并记为 $p_{i + }$ 。按照 $p_{i + }$ 的概率从 $x_{i}$ 中抽取 100 个样本，记为 $x_{1}^{*}, \\ldots, x_{100}^{*}$ 。",
            "2. 对 $k = 1, \\ldots, 100$ , 计算条件概率 $P(Y = y_{j} | X = x_{k}^{*})$ , 并记为 $p_{j \\mid k}^{*}$ 。按照 $p_{j \\mid k}^{*}$ 的概率从 $y_{j}$ 中抽取壹个样本, 并记为 $y_{k}^{*}$ 。",
            "3. 样本 $(x_{1}^{*}, y_{1}^{*}), \\ldots, (x_{100}^{*}, y_{100}^{*})$ 即为所得。"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            83,
            292,
            922,
            807
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二维离散型随机向量",
        "text_level": 1,
